import numpy as np
fc1 = Linear(4, 2)()
fc2 = Linear(4, 2)()
cadd = CAddTable()([fc1, fc2])
output1 = ReLU()(cadd)
model = Model([fc1, fc2], [output1])
fc1.element().set_weights([np.ones((4, 2)), np.ones((2,))])
fc2.element().set_weights([np.ones((4, 2)), np.ones((2,))])
output = model.forward([np.array([0.1, 0.2, -0.3, -0.4]), np.array([0.5, 
    0.4, -0.2, -0.1])])
assert_allclose(output, np.array([2.2, 2.2]))
